sequenceDiagram
        actor User as User
        participant WebUI as WebUI
        participant Server as Server
        participant Database as Database
        User->>+ WebUI: 1. Log out
        WebUI ->>+ Server: 2. POST / logout{}
        Server ->> +Database : 3. Destroy user session and token invalidation
        Database -->>- Server: 4. Acknowledge session termination
        Server -->>- WebUI : 5. 200 / {meta, message}
        WebUI -->>- User: 6. Redirect to login page
        opt Logout failed
            WebUI ->>+ Server: 2. POST / logout{}
            Server->> +Database : 3. Attempt to terminate user session
            Database -->>- Server: 4. Return failure / timeout
            Server -->>- WebUI : 5. 500 / {message}
            WebUI -->> User: 6. Display error message
        end
